summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 77E, Page 182 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property located within Section 31, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M. from Single Family Residence Medium Density (RS 7200) Zone to General Commercial (CG) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Barbo and Daniels Group, Donald B. Daniels, C.F. 289193).
